o</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Ilon Musk has announced plans to create his own 'AI game development studio. According to the businessman, “too many game studios are owned by large corporations” and so as part of the artificial intelligence startup xAI, he will “make games great again.”\nHowever, no other details about Musk's plans were forthcoming, nor was there any information from xAI.\nControversial enough, isn't it? xAI has raised $6 billion in Series B funding and could be valued at $40 billion. By comparison, Electronic Arts has a market value of $43 billion. By definition, game studio xAI would be run by .... a huge corporation.</p>\n<p><strong>We wish you a great mood!</strong></p>","wordCount":{"words":117}},"author":{"frontmatter":{"authorAlias":"Zakruzhnaya","author":"Olga Zakruzhnaya","authorPosition":"Marketing specialist","authorPhoto":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg","srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/40657/author.jpg 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/77b35/author.jpg 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/19e71/author.jpg 128w","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e8e20/author.avif 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/b6d61/author.avif 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/2e71d/author.avif 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/3c49f/author.avif 128w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e789a/author.webp 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/ef6ff/author.webp 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/8257c/author.webp 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/6766a/author.webp 128w","type":"i